'''沃森'''（{{lang-en|Watson}}）是能够使用[[自然语言|自然语言]]来回答问题的[[人工智能|人工智能]]系统，<ref name=ibm>{{cite | url=http://www.research.ibm.com/deepqa/faq.shtml | title=DeepQA Project: FAQ | publisher=IBM Corporation | accessdate=2011-02-11 | archive-date=2011-06-29 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629122514/http://www.research.ibm.com/deepqa/faq.shtml | dead-url=no }}</ref>由[[IBM|IBM]]公司的首席研究员{{tsl|en|David Ferrucci|大衛·費魯奇}}所领导的DeepQA计划小组开发并以该公司创始人[[托马斯·J·沃森|托马斯·J·沃森]]的名字命名。<ref name="NYT_20110208">{{cite | url = http://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/09/arts/television/09nova.html | title = Actors and Their Roles for $300, HAL? HAL! | first = Mike | last = Hale | publisher = The New York Times | date = 2011-02-08 | accessdate = 2011-08-19 | archive-date = 2012-03-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120329141326/http://www.nytimes.com/2011/02/09/arts/television/09nova.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite |url=http://www.research.ibm.com/deepqa/deepqa.shtml |title=The DeepQA Project |publisher=Research.ibm.com |date= |accessdate=2011-02-18 |archive-date=2011-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629122438/http://www.research.ibm.com/deepqa/deepqa.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年，沃森参加综艺节目《[[危险边缘|危险边缘]]》来测试它的能力，这是该节目有史以来第一次人与机器对决。<ref name="NYT_20110208" />2月14日至16日广播的3集节目中，沃森在前两轮中与对手打平，而在最后一集里，沃森打败了最高奖金得主{{link-en|布拉德·鲁特尔|Brad Rutter}}和连胜纪录保持者[[肯·詹宁斯|肯·詹宁斯]]。<ref>{{cite |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/27/technology/27jeopardy.html |title=Computer Program to Take On 'Jeopardy!' |last=Markoff |first=John |date=2009-04-26 |accessdate=2009-04-27 |work=The New York Times |authorlink=John Markoff |archive-date=2011-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110906084024/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/04/27/technology/27jeopardy.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite |url=http://gizmodo.com/#!5228887/ibm-prepping-soul+crushing-watson-computer-to-compete-on-jeopardy |title=IBM Prepping Soul-Crushing 'Watson' Computer to Compete on Jeopardy! |last=Loftus |first=Jack |date=2009-04-26 |publisher=Gizmodo |accessdate=2009-04-27 |archive-date=2013-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130207154205/http://gizmodo.com/#!5228887/ibm-prepping-soul+crushing-watson-computer-to-compete-on-jeopardy |dead-url=no }}</ref>沃森赢得了第一笔奖金100万美元，而肯·詹宁斯和布拉德·鲁特尔分别只有30万和20万。赛后，詹宁斯和鲁特表示将一半奖金用于慈善事业，IBM公司也将沃森的奖金分给了两家慈善机构。<ref>{{cite|title=IBM's "Watson" Computing System to Challenge All Time Greatest Jeopardy! Champions |url=http://www.jeopardy.com/news/watson1x7ap4.php |date=2010-12-14 |accessdate=2010-12-15 |publisher=Sony Pictures |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130616092431/http://www.jeopardy.com/news/watson1x7ap4.php |archivedate=2013-06-16 }}</ref>

