== 结构 ==
[[File:DeepQA.svg|350px]]

沃森是IBM制造的电脑问答（Q&A）系统。<ref name=ibm/> IBM介绍时说“它是一个集高级[[自然语言处理|自然语言处理]]、[[訊息检索|訊息检索]]、[[知识表示|知识表示]]、自动[[推理|推理]]、[[机器学习|机器学习]]等开放式问答技术的应用”<!--open domain question answering-->，并且“基于为假设认知<!--原文：hypothesis generation-->和大规模的证据搜集、分析、评价而开发的DeepQA技术”。<ref name=ibm/>

=== 硬件 ===
根据IBM的说法：
<blockquote>沃森是一台专为[[复杂分析|复杂分析]]而优化设计的系统，整合大规模[[并行处理器|并行处理器]]{{tsl|en|POWER7|}}和IBM DeepQA软件使其能在3秒内回答危险边缘的问题成为可能。沃森是由90台IBM [[Power_750|Power 750]]服务器（还包括10个机柜里额外的[[I/O|输入输出]]端口、网络和[[集群控制器|集群控制器]]节点）组成的[[集群服务器|集群服务器]]，共计2880颗POWER7处理器核心以及16TB[[内存|内存]]。每台Power 750服务器使用一个3.5GHz、8核心，每核心4[[线程|线程]]的POWER7处理器。只有POWER7处理器强大的并行计算能力才能勉强运行沃森安装的IBM DeepQA软件<!--原文：The POWER7 processor's massively parallel processing capability is an ideal match for Watson's IBM DeepQA software which is embarrassingly parallel-->。<ref>{{cite|url=http://www.cs.umbc.edu/2011/02/is-watson-the-smartest-machine-on-earth/|title=Is Watson the smartest machine on earth?|publisher=Computer Science and Electrical Engineering Department, UMBC|date=2011-02-10|accessdate=2011-02-11|archive-date=2011-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927014129/http://www.cs.umbc.edu/2011/02/is-watson-the-smartest-machine-on-earth/|dead-url=no}}</ref><!-- surely there's a more direct source of this presumed quote from IBM --></blockquote>
John Rennie说，沃森每秒可以处理500GB的数据，相当于1秒阅读100万本书。<ref name=rennie>{{cite | last = Rennie | first = John | url = http://blogs.plos.org/retort/2011/02/14/how-ibm%E2%80%99s-watson-computer-will-excel-at-jeopardy/ | title = How IBM’s Watson Computer Excels at Jeopardy! | publisher = PLoS blogs | date = 2011-02-14 | accessdate = 2011-02-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110222031017/http://blogs.plos.org/retort/2011/02/14/how-ibm%E2%80%99s-watson-computer-will-excel-at-jeopardy/ | archive-date = 2011-02-22 | dead-url = yes }}</ref> IBM研发负责人和高级[[顾问|顾问]]Tony Pearson估计沃森的硬件花费近300万美元，<ref>{{cite | last = Lucas | first = Mearian | url = http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9210381/Can_anyone_afford_an_IBM_Watson_supercomputer_Yes_?taxonomyId=67&pageNumber=2 | title = Can anyone afford an IBM Watson supercomputer?（Yes） | publisher = [[Computerworld|Computerworld]] | date = 2011-02-21 | accessdate = 2011-02-21 | archive-date = 2013-12-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212014259/http://www.computerworld.com/s/article/9210381/Can_anyone_afford_an_IBM_Watson_supercomputer_Yes_?taxonomyId=67&pageNumber=2 | dead-url = no }}</ref>其80 [[TeraFLOPs|TeraFLOPs]]的处理能力在[[超级电脑|超级电脑]][[TOP500|世界500强]]排名第94，在超级电脑世界50强排名第49。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/mydeveloperworks/blogs/InsideSystemStorage/?lang=en |title=Tony Pearson's blog |access-date=2011-08-19 |archive-date=2019-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006090113/https://www.ibm.com/developerworks/mydeveloperworks/blogs/InsideSystemStorage/?lang=en |dead-url=no }}</ref> Rennie还说，比赛的数据是存放在沃森的内存中的，因为[[硬盘|硬盘]]的存取速度太慢了。<ref name=rennie/>

=== 软體 ===
